  "instructions": [
    "Heat a pan with olive oil and sauté the onion until translucent.",
    "Add lemon peel, peppercorn, and lentils to the pan. Stir for about 5 minutes.",
    "Pour in rice and mix well. Add piccalilli and mix thoroughly.",
    "If using sous-vide, place the dish in a water bath at 160°F (72°C) for an hour.",
    "In a separate pan, simmer lemon juice with saffron until thickened. Pour over the pilaf.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds on top and serve hot."
